text: Jessica Rose "Jessie" James Decker (born April 12, 1988) is an Italian- American country-pop singer-songwriter. Her first album, Jessie James, was released in August of 2009. Jessie James was born in Vicenza, Italy. ==References== Category:American country musicians Category:American pop singers Category:American singer-songwriters Category:Italian singers Category:People from Vicenza Category:1988 births
